did.abstract: This is a collection of undergraduate student papers. Some undergraduate courses require a final paper or thesis in lieu of a final exam.

custodhist.head: Provenance
custodhist.p: Transferred from John Briggs on the WCSU Writing Department in the Summer of 2010.
